name: The Sun
description:
- 3D Sun Art - 
The Sun is the star at the center of the Solar System and its size is 109 times the earth. The Sun's core fuses about 600 million tons of hydrogen into helium every second, converting 4 million tons of matter into energy every second as a result. This energy, which can take between 10,000 and 170,000 years to escape the core, is the source of the Sun's light and heat.
